Lucille McVey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucille_McVey 0 Lucille McVey (April 18, 1890, Sedalia, Missouri – November 3, 1925) also known as Mrs Sidney Drew, was an American screenwriter, director, producer and actress. In the early 1900s, she was part with her husband Sidney Drew of the famous comedy duo Mr. and Mrs. Sidney Drew.
